      {
        "paragraph_index": 2,
        "text": "### Largest Network: ref_eq_net_5023\n\nThis network covers near-room-temperature, low-ionic-strength conditions and contains **3 VLM nodes** representing three equilibrium reactions:\n\n| VLM Node | Reaction | log K |\n|---|---|---|\n| (beta_def_812) | Ni²⁺ + L⁴⁻ ⇌ [NiL]²⁻ | **18.4** |\n| (beta_def_788) | [NiL]²⁻ + H⁺ ⇌ [NiHL]⁻ | 3.1 |\n| (beta_def_966) | [Ni(OH)L]³⁻ + H⁺ ⇌ [NiL]²⁻ + H₂O | −11.9 |\n\nThe full VLM IDs from the system catalog span **vlm_108585 through vlm_108603** (19 total measurements across all 4 beta definitions), with the 3 nodes of ref_eq_net_5023 drawn from the subset covering beta_def_812, beta_def_788, and beta_def_966.\n\n> **Note:** The exact per-node VLM IDs for ref_eq_net_5023 could not be retrieved due to a schema table name mismatch (`equilibrium_network_node` not found). The network structure and reaction data above are confirmed from SRD-46.",
